  "title": "Hair Stylist",
  "description": "<p>Hair Stylist (Full-Time) 美发师（全职）</p><p>📍 Location: Clementi Mall 地点：金文泰 商场</p><p><br /></p><p>What You’ll Do 你的工作内容</p><p>Provide professional haircuts, styling, washing, coloring & hair treatment services</p><p>提供专业剪发、造型、洗发、染发及护理服务</p><p><br /></p><p>Consult with clients to understand their style preferences and hair condition</p><p>与客户沟通，了解其风格喜好与发质状况</p><p><br /></p><p>Recommend suitable styles, treatments or products based on customer needs</p><p>根据客户需求推荐合适发型、疗程或产品</p><p><br /></p><p>Maintain salon hygiene and ensure proper use of tools and equipment</p><p>保持工作区域整洁，工具使用规范</p><p><br /></p><p>Upsell packages or products when appropriate</p><p>适时推荐套餐或护理产品，提高客户满意度</p><p><br /></p><p>Who We’re Looking For 我们希望你具备：</p><p>Minimum 2 years of hairdressing experience in a salon environment</p><p>至少2年美发沙龙工作经验</p><p><br /></p><p>Able to communicate in English and Mandarin</p><p>能用英文与中文沟通（需服务双语客户）</p><p><br /></p><p>Skilled in haircutting, coloring and/or treatment services</p><p>熟练掌握剪发、染发或发质护理技术</p><p><br /></p><p>Friendly, service-oriented and confident in giving style advice</p><p>有亲和力，服务意识强，能主动提供造型建议</p><p><br /></p><p>Willing to work on weekends and public holidays</p><p>可配合周末及假日轮班</p><p><br /></p><p>Bonus if you have 加分条件：</p><p>Experience with scalp treatments or perm services</p><p>有头皮护理或烫发经验更佳</p><p><br /></p><p>Strong personal client base</p><p>拥有个人客户群者优先</p><p><br /></p><p>Familiar with Japanese / Korean style cuts or trends</p><p>熟悉日韩发型风格者优先</p><p><br /></p><p>Why Join Us? 加入我们的理由</p><p>Positive, supportive salon culture and team</p><p>团队氛围轻松有爱，互相支持成长</p><p><br /></p><p>Salary with commission – no income ceiling!</p><p>薪资+提成，收入不设限！</p><p><br /></p><p>Convenient central location near MRT</p><p>交通便利，近裕廊东地铁站</p><p><br /></p><p>Career growth opportunities and advanced training provided</p><p>提供技术进修与晋升空间</p><p><br /></p><p>Ready to Style with Us? 准备一起变美变强了吗？</p><p>📞 WhatsApp us at +65 9858 0286</p>",
